Create a function that will take a String value as first parameter, Number value as second and String value as third.
First parameter should be a sentence or set of sentences, second parameter should be a number
of letter in each word in the sentence that should be replaced by the third parameter. That function should return updated sentence.  

let str = 'Xochy yehat na Sri Lanky, a ne vot eto vot vse';
let newstr = str.split("")
 for (let i = 2; i < newstr.length; i=i+3)
 {
	newstr[i]='Yes';
 }
	console.log(newstr.join(''));
